text:
Located in Leisure Farm, surrounded in green. Its a place for simple breakfast or lunch.

I enjoyed a pack of nasi lemak with fried chicken thigh during a weekday morning. I heard the birds singing, enjoyed the fresh air and the food was tasty too.

During my stay, there was a kitten accompany me throughout my lunch.
A simple fast and one stop small food u can grab if u dont want to rush to get munch outside area.
Cheap and good nasi lemak. I had breakfast here. Reminds me of kampung days.
